rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0001
rows.name:
You seem awfully quiet.
Did you get seasick or something?

rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm just...not used to ships with this
many salvagers on, that's all!

rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, if it's wearing you out now,
you'll be a wreck by the time we
reach our destination.

rows.label: tlk0001024_msg0005
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]I can handle myself, all right?!
